assert value.is_multipart == expected_value
pytest.mark.parametrize('value,expected_value', [[Range('bytes', [RangePart
    (100, None)]), False], [Range('bytes', [RangePart(100, 200), RangePart(
    400, 600)]), True], [Range('bytes', [RangePart(100, 200), RangePart(400,
    600), RangePart(300, 500)]), True]])
